{"tid":25753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本跟隨歐美，不承認中國市場經濟地位","createTime":"2016-12-06T10:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T07:19:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a3bac01b95c759c1bd711b94c3ee35ffe5ae31","tid":25753,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:12:19.000Z","msg":"日媒:日與歐美同步不承認中國市場經濟國地位 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2016/12/06/1448860_838ee73dee963ed7114bf6b96e62d2b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F06%2F1448860_838ee73dee963ed7114bf6b96e62d2b2.jpg&h=52aabc46&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1448860/%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92%3A%E6%97%A5%E8%88%87%E6%AD%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A5%E4%B8%8D%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1448860%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AA%2592%253A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25AD%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BD%258D&d=KBvGWA0y16EJK01kwjhrPGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=8f11878b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1448860/%E6%97%A5%E5%AA%92%3A%E6%97%A5%E8%88%87%E6%AD%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A5%E4%B8%8D%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D</a> <br />\n<br />\n日本《讀賣新聞》報道，日本政府已經基本決定，將與歐洲及美國保持同步，不承認中國「市場經濟國」地位。 <br />\n<br />\n報道又指出，日本首相安倍晉三在參議院上稱，中國國有企業的「不當傾銷」行為，損害市場秩序。安倍指出，中國鋼鐵業產能過剩，並以相當低廉的價格對外銷售，這讓全球鋼鐵企業及相關企業深受其害。"},{"pid":"3c8a4f367a599327a7dc51bce2b8d3a5df80b905","tid":25753,"uid":997,"like":0,"d